  notes:
    - "This spec covers: threading.Event.__name__ 'Event'; threading.Event.__module__ 'threading'; threading.Event.__bases__[0].__name__ 'object'; threading.Condition.__name__ 'Condition'; threading.Condition.__module__ 'threading'; threading.Condition.__bases__[0].__name__ 'object'; threading.Semaphore.__name__ 'Semaphore'; threading.Semaphore.__module__ 'threading'; threading.Semaphore.__bases__[0].__name__ 'object' (Wave 295)."
