    - "threading.Event.__bases__[0].__name__ == 'object' — threading.Event inherits directly from object; its __bases__[0].__name__ is 'object'. Verified with Python 3.14.3."
    - "threading.Condition.__name__ == 'Condition' — threading.Condition is a Python class defined in Lib/threading.py implementing a condition variable synchronization primitive; its class __name__ is 'Condition'. Verified with Python 3.14.3."
    - "threading.Condition.__module__ == 'threading' — Condition is defined in Lib/threading.py; its __module__ attribute is 'threading'. Verified with Python 3.14.3."
    - "threading.Condition.__bases__[0].__name__ == 'object' — threading.Condition inherits directly from object; its __bases__[0].__name__ is 'object'. Verified with Python 3.14.3."
    - "threading.Semaphore.__name__ == 'Semaphore' — threading.Semaphore is a Python class defined in Lib/threading.py implementing a counting semaphore; its class __name__ is 'Semaphore'. Verified with Python 3.14.3."
    - "threading.Semaphore.__module__ == 'threading' — Semaphore is defined in Lib/threading.py; its __module__ attribute is 'threading'. Verified with Python 3.14.3."
    - "threading.Semaphore.__bases__[0].__name__ == 'object' — threading.Semaphore inherits directly from object; its __bases__[0].__name__ is 'object'. Verified with Python 3.14.3."
